{"tid":509681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊仔爬牆避追捕 跌落「撩陰掃把」直插胸","createTime":"2017-12-25T14:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T15:16:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e58ca4b520b12537396b0204837bcdc621da2745","tid":509681,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171225/20255068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F20255068&d=4wIt%2FDyNivndORFNwZq2V%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2727ce6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F20255068&h=f34bfef8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171225/20255068</a><br />\n<br />\n賊仔爬牆避追捕<br />\n跌落「撩陰掃把」直插胸<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴西發生一宗駭人案件，一名男子為了躲避警察，翻牆跳入一戶住宅，怎料落地位置剛好有一把掃帚，結果柄身木棍從他陰囊插入，穿過腹部再從胸口穿出，情狀恐怖。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁「Cidade Nova &ndash; Ananindeua/Par&aacute;」日前分享這宗事件，地點相信是在巴西東北部大城市貝倫。專頁的上載了該名男子之後動手術的片段，同樣十分駭人。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，醫生拉開男子的陰囊，把掃帚木棍由下方往上推，讓木棍慢慢從胸部整支退出來，看著都感到毛骨悚然。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《詩華日報》"},{"pid":"78b713924f2d424fa1836b183663d39af85eb7e7","tid":509681,"uid":41174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗到都痛"},{"pid":"1572ad0491c5a271bf04106c2e74cdd6a151a558","tid":509681,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"冇圖?"}]}